headline: More Than Two-Thirds Of Gen Z Values Financial Responsibility From Their Potential Partners
summary: There are a lot of things to consider when choosing a romantic partner, but financial responsibility is one of the most important factors. That insight comes from "A Window into Gen Z's Financial Health," a report prepared for Bank of America (NYSE:BAC) earlier this year. The report found that 78% of Gen Z places financial responsibility on a high pedestal when assessing a potential partner. headline: Are Robinhood Shares Justified After BofA's Raised $119 Price Target and Surging 2025 Rally?
summary: If you have been watching Robinhood Markets stock lately, you are not alone. Whether you are considering its notable 161% return so far this year or thinking back on the impressive 406.5% rise over the past twelve months, it would be hard not to stop and wonder what is driving this momentum and whether it is likely to continue. Of course, it has not all been smooth sailing. Robinhood slipped by 2.3% over the past week and dipped 3.6% in the last 30 days. Such swings might feel like simple...
